@startuml
class Flyweight(享元模式) {
  class FlyweightFactory {
    -mMap:HashMap
    +getFlyweight()
  }
  class Flyweight {
    +dosomething()
  }
  class ConcreteFlyweight {
    -intrinsicState:String
    +dosomething()
  }
}

FlyweightFactory --> Flyweight : 组合
Flyweight <|-- ConcreteFlyweight : 继承

note right of FlyweightFactory : 享元工厂
note right of Flyweight : 享元对象抽象基类或者接口
note right of ConcreteFlyweight : 具体的享元对象

@enduml
